		<li id="comment_134665">
			
			<!-- Moderation? -->
			
			<p>It&#8217;s entirely possible to convert a thick-body iPod to a thin-body one by replacing the hard drive and backplate with those from a thin model.  As far as I&#8217;m aware, this works for all iPod generations with two thicknesses.  It does not work cross-generation, as internal layouts vary.</p>
			
			<div class="meta">
				<div class="left">
					<strong><cite><a href='http://www.command-tab.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Collin</a></cite></strong>
